{"data":[{"date":"07:54 17/07","title":"Mourinho: \u201cRonaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Man Utd ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Serie A sau khi Juventus n\u1ed5 qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/hanh-dong-thu-vi-cua-ronaldo-khi-gioi-thieu-ao-dau-tai-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real sang Juventus, v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh xung quanh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi Serie A gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV c\u1ee7a Man Utd cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng phanh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t: \u201cLa Liga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Italia. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 Premier League, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u00ean gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n ki\u1ec1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem La Liga v\u00ec c\u00f3 Messi, xem Serie A v\u00ec c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 xem Premier League v\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tinh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m v\u1ecb th\u1ebf, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng cho Juventus, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd, t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh. Ngh\u0129 m\u00e0 xem nh\u1eefng Roma, Napoli, AC Milan v\u00e0 Inter Milan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau so v\u1edbi Juve.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4281","checkdouble":"191396"},{"date":"08:40 17/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 17/7: Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-177-ronaldo-vo-tinh-bao-hai-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Ronaldo, Real quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Bale</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 177 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 177 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gareth Bale</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edbi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng CR7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Man Utd v\u1ed1n tham v\u1ecdng nghi\u00eam t\u00fac chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chia tay m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c sang Juventus. V\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Gareth Bale v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City b\u1ecb Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u1ee5 sao Croatia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 177 Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 177 Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-177-Ronaldo-vo-tinh-bao-hai-Man-Utd-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mateo Kovacic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb Fred sang Man Utd \u0111\u1ebfn Jorginho sang Man City, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e0nh l\u00f2ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u1edf Bernabeu n\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng t\u1ed9i g\u00ec Real Madrid ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh, ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Daley Blind<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Daley Blind</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Old Trafford, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i Daley Blind cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lyon ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Fekir\" title=\"tien ve Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nabil Fekir</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh Lyon c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ed1n \u0111ang su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Liverpool v\u00ec l\u00fd do m\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 l\u1eb1ng nh\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Nabil Fekir. Gi\u1edd sau khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00f9ng Merseyside trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u00ednh cu\u1ed7m Higuain kh\u1ecfi Juventus<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gonzalo Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mang th\u00eam c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u00ean \u00dd v\u1ec1 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf m\u1edbi \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Chelsea v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Cristiano Ronaldo, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3. El Pipita \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Golovin\" title=\"Alex Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Aleksandr Golovin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi Liverpool t\u0103m tia Domagoj Vida, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi Dejan Lovren \u1edf Anfield, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng duy\u1ec7t chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00ec Aleksandr Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Monaco l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ednh nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec3n trai ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb gh\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t Croatia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalinic bi duoi co ve nuoc\" title=\"Kalinic b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ed1 v\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hoc-tay-ban-nha-croatia-duoi-nguoi-ngay-thoi-diem-dien-ra-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nikola Kalinic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Diego Simeone mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sau khi chia tay Fernando Torres. C\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng ng\u1eafm ngh\u00eda l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Nikola Kalinic, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018 can t\u1ed9i\u2026 ch\u1ea3nh. Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AC Milan nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4280","checkdouble":"191403"},{"date":"07:23 17/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri: \u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5-6 Chelsea \u1edf Anh\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-hlv-sarri-van-de-cho-toi-la-co-den-56-chelsea-o-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean gh\u00e9 n\u00f3ng Stamford Bridge.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia \u0111\u00f4i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi Antonio Conte sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup, Chelsea nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a CLB. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Maurizio Sarri</span> sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Napoli gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/chelsea-sap-chao-don-4-tan-binh-duoi-thoi-sarri.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Sarri nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Anh. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Sarri c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho t\u00f4i l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5-6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m g\u00ec Chelsea, trong khi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00edt s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u1edf \u00dd.\u201d \u2013 Sarri nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh nh\u00f3m Big Six kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, trong khi \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus hay c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm Roma \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o Chelsea m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nhau v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.\u201d \u2013 Sarri s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Inter Milan, Arsenal v\u00e0 Lyon. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/_102527296_jorginho_getty2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4279","checkdouble":"191394"},{"date":"08:49 17/07","title":"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi M.U c\u1ee7a Mourinho?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi HLV Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic ch\u01b0a quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Man United</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2017, tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra sau khi c\u00e1c b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u0103m nay, M.U \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Perisic sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Man United khi t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Mourinho tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Mourinho, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Perisic c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Croatia m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup\u00a02018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United \u00e0? L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 d\u00e0nh cho Croatia. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung cho CLB Inter Milan\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Perisic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh cho th\u1ea5y anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Inter. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Nerazzurri c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 6/2022.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia-184-191267.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia-184-191267.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/07: MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4278","checkdouble":"191400"},{"date":"18:54 16/07","title":"Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim hi\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Pavle Balenovic c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 29 n\u0103m ghi l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Croatia, n\u01a1i Luka Modric \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i hoang d\u00e3.\r\n</h2><div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/modric.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay, v\u1eeba tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00c1 qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ai bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Luka Modric t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tu\u1ed5i th\u01a1 ngh\u00e8o kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua, \u0111o\u1ea1n phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m phim Pavle Balenovic thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc quay t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990 k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ea7y c\u1eebu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n ch\u00f3 s\u00f3i tr\u00ean ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai Velebit hi\u1ec3m tr\u1edf quanh th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n nh\u1ecf Jasenice \u1edf Zadar, m\u1ed9t v\u00f9ng \u1edf mi\u1ec1n nam Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u00fa b\u00e9 ch\u0103n d\u00ea xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong b\u1ed9 phim v\u1edbi d\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh lo\u1eaft cho\u1eaft, m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o kho\u00e1c qu\u00e1 kh\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc nhanh tho\u0103n tho\u1eaft tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh n\u00fai hi\u1ec3m tr\u1edf, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cha l\u00f9a \u0111\u00e0n d\u00ea v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh m\u1eaft r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n s\u00f3i hoang d\u00e3.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/5b4a8eb8fc7e9330298b4632.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim hi\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 ch\u00fa b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fa b\u00e9 Luka ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 d\u00e0nh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u s\u1ed1ng trong gi\u1eefa n\u00fai r\u1eebng quanh nh\u1eefng b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby hi\u1ec3m nguy. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho BBC, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo l\u1eddi Balenovic k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y, \u00f4ng l\u00e0m quen v\u00e0 t\u1edbi th\u0103m gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Stipe Modric, cha c\u1ee7a Luka m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n l\u00ean n\u00fai. Sau n\u0103m 1990, chi\u1ebfn tranh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh Modrid ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tr\u00ean n\u00fai Velebit.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u1edbc phim v\u1ec1 ch\u00fa b\u00e9 Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n d\u00ea gi\u1eefa b\u00e0y s\u00f3i hoang d\u00e3 M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay t\u1ea1i Zadar, Croatia n\u0103m 1990 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Luka Modric ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u0103n d\u00ea gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 gia \u0111\u00ecnh gi\u1eefa n\u00fai r\u1eebng hi\u1ec3m tr\u1edf<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n 30 n\u0103m, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka lo\u1eaft cho\u1eaft ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o v\u1eabn trong h\u00ecnh h\u00e0i nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 nh\u01b0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00ednh qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, hi\u1ec3m nguy \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea1y cho Luka l\u00f2ng can tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 \u00fd ch\u00ed s\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u01b0\u01a1n ra ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi Croatia, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, La Liga.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4277","checkdouble":"191375"},{"date":"21:03 16/07","title":"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri \u00e2n theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/paris-doi-ten-6-tram-tau-dien-ngam-de-ghi-nho-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4276","checkdouble":"191377"},{"date":"21:29 16/07","title":"C\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t 12 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u00ec Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t 79 tri\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n t\u1ec7 (NDT) v\u00ec tr\u00f3t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec tin Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Reuters, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng 79 tri\u1ec7u NDT (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 12 tri\u1ec7u USD) v\u00ec Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. C\u00f4ng ty Vatti c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng \u0110\u00f4ng (Trung Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean Weibo (m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c) c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, c\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t 12 tri\u1ec7u USD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, c\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t 12 tri\u1ec7u USD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/cong-ty-trung-quoc-mat-12-trieu-usd-vi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t 12 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u00ec c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Vatti cung c\u1ea5p &quot;g\u00f3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&quot; tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 16.100 NDT bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ebfp ga, m\u00e1y \u0111un n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 m\u00e1y r\u1eeda b\u00e1t v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb 1/6-3/7 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n mua &quot;g\u00f3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&quot; trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, Vatti cho bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng may m\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Reuters, c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Vatti \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng 10% trong th\u1ee9 Hai, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 m\u1ea5t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i Vatti nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia kinh t\u1ebf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Weibo b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea5t mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho h\u1ecd sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Vatti ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Weibo trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br />\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/paris-doi-ten-6-tram-tau-dien-ngam-de-ghi-nho-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-465-191377.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri \u00e2n theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/phap-da-tran-yem-san-luznhiki-truoc-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-188-191354.html\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n y\u1ec3m s\u00e2n Luznhiki tr\u01b0\u1edbc chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/hanh-dong-khac-thuong-cua-pogba-o-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-188-191353.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\">H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4275","checkdouble":"191378"},{"date":"23:04 16/07","title":"Juventus b\u00e1n 520 ngh\u00ecn \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ra m\u1eaft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin, Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus b\u00e1n 520 ngh\u00ecn \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Turin trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Cr7 nh\u01b0ng ngay trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfm b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus ban 520 nghin ao dau nho Cristiano Ronaldo.\" title=\"Juventus b\u00e1n 520 ngh\u00ecn \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd Cristiano Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Juventus b\u00e1n 520 ngh\u00ecn \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd Cristiano Ronaldo.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Turin, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 520.000 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd qua. \u00c1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 104 euro v\u00e0 44.9 euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Juventus ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i \u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra trong ng\u00e0y qua. \u1ede m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh 74.45 euro, Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 38.7 tri\u1ec7u euro, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1n s\u1ed1t Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Italia, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef &quot;CR7&quot; cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-465-191363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/Nhung-hinh-anh-ve-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-465-191363.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u00e1n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u khi Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m 2016. Trong c\u1ea3 n\u0103m, Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 850.000 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u trong khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 Ronaldo, &quot;b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&quot; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c con s\u1ed1 g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Neymar \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Paris Saint Germain, \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng &quot;ch\u1ec9&quot; c\u00f3 10.000 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e1i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-suyt-toi-napoli-thay-vi-juventus-176-191263.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo-180-191111.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4274","checkdouble":"191382"},{"date":"00:11 17/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. Juventus c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi, m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>&quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Real Madrid, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eafng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac cho th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 di chy\u1ec3n n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf Italia r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf trong v\u00f9ng an to\u00e0n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Manchester United. Real Madrid v\u00e0 gi\u1edd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m  m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec? Ng\u1ed3i qu\u1ea9n quanh  tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf \u1edf nh\u00e0 \u01b0? T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u1eadt ch\u0103m  ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>Mang Champions League \u0111\u1ebfn cho Juventus</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Champions League m\u00e0  Scudetto c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i  b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3  m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 xem chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-465-191363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/Nhung-hinh-anh-ve-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-465-191363.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh  t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 th\u1eadt vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o  \u0111\u00f3n&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>T\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real Madrid t\u1eeb bao gi\u1edd?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Gi\u1edd vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0  tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions  League \u1edf Kiev. T\u00f4i kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng  m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng \u1edf Juventus</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2  hai 3 l\u1ea7n, gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 5. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u1edf Manchester United v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3  l\u00e0 Real Madrid, t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee9?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Nh\u1eefng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac&quot;.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1o ra \u1edf Juventus</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn, th\u1eadt vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u1edf  \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i  b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t h\u01a1n&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf  t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat-465-191382.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat-465-191382.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 520 ngh\u00ecn \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ra m\u1eaft</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin, Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tranh lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m  \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00edch so s\u00e1nh t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Messi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0  m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i di\u1ec5n ra ngay v\u00e0o  ng\u00e0y mai. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb k\u00edch th\u00edch b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn  Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1&quot;.</p>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-suyt-toi-napoli-thay-vi-juventus-176-191263.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo-180-191111.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4273","checkdouble":"191385"},{"date":"05:28 17/07","title":"Sao Juventus n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00e2n binh Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/052147-1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can sau khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 30 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d th\u00e0nh Turin</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/m\u00f9a.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emre Can n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emre Can n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/052147-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c C\u0110V m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1eeb Liverpool theo d\u1ea1ng t\u1ef1 do, nh\u01b0ng Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u00e0 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i CR7:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh n\u00ean c\u1ea3 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Juventus ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 \u2018h\u1ed5 m\u1ecdc th\u00eam c\u00e1nh\u2019. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 CR7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bayern Munich, Benfica, MLS All-Stars v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (ng\u00e0y 4/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4272","checkdouble":"191387"},{"date":"20:15 16/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/7: Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/diem-tin-toi-167-sao-tre-mbappe-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp hai ng\u00f4i sao World Cup,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Arsenal tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Ozil xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 do \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 167 Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 167 Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/mbappe-nhan-gui-real-madrid-sau-khi-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kylian Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Kylian Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;100% \u1edf l\u1ea1i Paris Saint Germain khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan khi V-League 2018 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u1ec3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Emre Can th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh h\u1ea1nh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Cristiano Ronaldo trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &quot;h\u00edp&quot; b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2022 di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Qatar l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1i n\u00f3ng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, FIFA \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc c\u00f3 n\u00ean t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 48 hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adil Rami v\u1eeba tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 35 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung Min them mot lan nua bo lo co hoi ghi ban. Anh: \u200bFIFA.\" title=\"Son Heung Min th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1edf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ea2nh: \u200bFIFA.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/985249586-5674-1530114089_600x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung Min s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u00eam hai ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 Son Heung-min v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jo Hyeon-woo - ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft 102 ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ee5 b\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1n b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t sau khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Nga, Vladimir Putin cho bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Nga d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n visa \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi-188-191375.html\">Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim hi\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/benjamin-pavard-va-nhung-cai-ten-hoa-rong-sau-vck-world-cup-2018-421-191374.html\">Benjamin Pavard v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean 'h\u00f3a r\u1ed3ng' sau VCK World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/raktic-tu-hao-ve-nguoi-anh-em-modric-sau-ky-tich-cua-croatia-421-191371.html\">Raktic t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em Modric sau k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-191370.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff-172-191368.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4271","checkdouble":"191376"},{"date":"18:58 16/07","title":"Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas c\u1ee7a Lyon m\u1edbi b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai cho Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh Nabil Fekir.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nabil Fekir n\u0103m nay 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lyon v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 24 b\u00e0n/28 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ligue 1, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1eb1ng su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p chia tay n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fekir t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111i\u00eau luy\u1ec7n, nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc b\u00e9n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lyon xu\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Liverpool mua Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lyon xu\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Liverpool mua Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lyon xu\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Liverpool mua Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n anh l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 quan v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00f3 h\u1eadu, The Kop b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb Lyon d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Lyon b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u201cc\u00f9 nh\u1ea7y\u201d th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 trong chuy\u1ec7n m\u1eafc c\u1ea3, th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 mua Fekir, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Anfield. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i The Kop:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 g\u00ec h\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Fekir ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi chuy\u1ec7n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Liverpool c\u0169ng\u2026 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m n\u1eefa, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao Xherdan Shaqiri</span> t\u1eeb Stoke City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ldbd-phap-xac-nhan-liverpool-sap-no-them-bom-tan-172-188138.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Ph\u00e1p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Liverpool s\u1eafp n\u1ed5 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lyon-chinh-thuc-xac-minh-thuc-hu-vu-liverpool-mua-fekir-172-188158.html\">Lyon ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c minh th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Fekir</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4270","checkdouble":"191370"},{"date":"21:46 16/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong su\u1ed1t k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Inter Milan \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u0103m nay, khi m\u00e0 Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, M.U c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford n\u00ean s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Perisic t\u1eeb Inter Milan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. Perisic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Antonio Valencia b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, M.U \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Juan Mata, Jesse Lingard, Anthony Martial v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m song kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ai cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p khi \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic 3 l\u00fd do MU c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic 3 l\u00fd do MU c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/4/Ivan-Perisic-3-ly-do-MU-can-chieu-mo-ngay-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic s\u1ebd th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng gh\u00e9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Perisic s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a M.U. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 v\u1edbi Perisic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tung ra t\u1edbi 197 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua t\u1ea1i Milan, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u01b0a th\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M.U b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi Ivan Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao Croatia r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi trong c\u00e1c pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Nh\u1edd chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1m86 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Perisic d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c pha nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi M.U trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hay nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Ivan Perisic c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c pha tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft l\u00f9i b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Icardi va Perisic (phai) toa sang\" title=\"Icardi v\u00e0 Perisic (ph\u1ea3i) t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/21/Chelsea-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-tien-dao-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic (ph\u1ea3i) l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 29, Perisic \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u1ea1i Inter Milan, Perisci kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh m\u00e0 anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e3 ghi 11 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 8 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Sang m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Perisic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam 11 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 9 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. T\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic\" title=\"Perisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-HLV-Mourinho-muon-MU-chieu-mo-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Perisic c\u0169ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Perisic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u00f3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Mourinho, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i M.U. V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 M.U l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Inter Milan trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-thu-co-the-thay-the-hazard-tai-chelsea-172-191365.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/5-cau-thu-co-the-thay-the-hazard-tai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-thu-co-the-thay-the-hazard-tai-chelsea-172-191365.html\">5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Hazard t\u1ea1i Chelsea</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Real nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\">99% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Daley Blind r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-167-187-191337.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ngay-hom-nay-167.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-167-187-191337.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 16/7: MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alex Sandro</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (16/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4269","checkdouble":"191381"}]}